{"tid":2391092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛：與中國官員有良好有成效的討論","createTime":"2021-02-02T03:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T04:07:39.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fcca3a78ca40472d6f30418bbd0dbf2f25472c2b","tid":2391092,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:48:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573539-20210202.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573539-20210202.htm&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BHr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=cb321368\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573539-20210202.htm&h=b24c2209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573539-20210202.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n實情就係比軍人脅持住咁行預定路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 參觀武肺博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 禁止接觸當地人 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道說，WHO發言人周五表示，由於健康方面的限制措施，該小組在武漢的接觸僅限於由中國東道主組織的訪問，而不會與當地社區交流。<br />\n「團隊會出去，但他們會被巴士送到所有地方，所以他們不會和社區有任何接觸，」世衛組織發言人瑪格麗特&middot;哈里斯（Margaret Harris）周五在日內瓦的一次簡報會上說。「他們只會接觸到被組織的與研究有關的各種人。」<br />\n「非常重要的第一次實地考察。我們在治療一些已知最早病例的醫院裏，與從事這項工作的實際臨牀醫生和工作人員會面，公開討論他們工作的細節，」世衛團隊成員彼得&middot;達扎克（Peter Daszak）在推特上寫道。<br />\n該團隊計劃在剩下的兩周內訪問武漢的實驗室、市場和醫院。2019年底，新冠病毒在武漢首次被發現。<br />\nBBC駐中國記者麥笛文（Stephen McDonell）從武漢現場報道說，由於世衛組織團隊的行程並不公開，當他們離開酒店時，大量媒體車輛試圖跟隨他們的車隊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20210130/s00053/19aaf536df087a68b4758d87f84049de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20210130%2Fs00053%2F19aaf536df087a68b4758d87f84049de.jpg&h=c948f35f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/68267974-64d7-11eb-b1e4-005056a98db9/w:1280/p:16x9/2021-02-01T054127Z_1750164771_RC2HJL9IOWKC_RTRMADP_3_HEALTH-CORONAVIRUS-WHO-CHINA.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F68267974-64d7-11eb-b1e4-005056a98db9%2Fw%3A1280%2Fp%3A16x9%2F2021-02-01T054127Z_1750164771_RC2HJL9IOWKC_RTRMADP_3_HEALTH-CORONAVIRUS-WHO-CHINA.webp&h=9950b6c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"697df7d25f9e58606c118ac917335dfbb17acba8","tid":2391092,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1a1499383d6a896ea8ff643c47b78cb3d29459","tid":2391092,"uid":264362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"好似join左北韓旅行團咁"},{"pid":"912ab0c3b88f58a1e588de340f1fd4d4fd12434a","tid":2391092,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:51:23.000Z","msg":"脅持世衛人質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2081b4d900755b6630eb4ef7a21b72dfcf3401c2","tid":2391092,"uid":170765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"旅行團?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e48edb8bd0766f38b66a7e435d6abc3e65c521","tid":2391092,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:54:44.000Z","msg":"大家都做緊戲姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a358bf6402126ecb2c8bdcf45a2d388ddec589","tid":2391092,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:00:24.000Z","msg":"有冇親密性交流?"},{"pid":"351fd894e69cacd3858ebf1944b3be6a88b3c75f","tid":2391092,"uid":42978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2081b4d900755b6630eb4ef7a21b72dfcf3401c2","tid":2391092,"uid":170765,"like"